document_data.Geography:
Soorenar was located on the coast of the Bay of Chessenta at the delta of the [[River Akax]], which split the city into East Soorenar&mdash;where the docks, warehouses, and amenities for mercenaries were located&mdash;and the well-defended West Soorenar&mdash;where most of the city's residents lived. Its location made it one of the primary Chessentan ports on the [[Inner Sea]].

Following the lowering of the Inner Sea as a result of the Spellplague and the opening of the [[Underchasm]], the Bay of Chessenta shrank, thus leaving Drowned Soorenar fairly far inland along the River Akax on very the eastern edge of the newly formed [[Lake Akax]].{{Cite dungeon/178/Backdrop: Chessenta|72}}

[[Mudmen]] were known to be especially numerous in the shallow waters north of the city.
